post-0.1


1) move to wxPython 2.6.x
2) move to PostgreSQL 8.x


- configurable buttons in gui helpers message windows

database API:
- re-evaluate DB-API drivers
- make PgArray into a stub
- move to psycopg ?
	- only if it supports NOTIFY/LISTEN
	- pyPgSQL is not well-maintained

database schema:
	- grant access to treatment teams
	- hide data from unrelated treatment teams
	- soap_cat domain
	- gender domain
	- laterality domain
	- session-temporary setting of curr_lang
	- support "care team" and row level ACLs (nested groups ?)
	- coded_term: trigger on delete: restrict if term in clin_root_item.narrative

client startup:
	- gnumed.py: rework use of resource_dir/base_dir

EMR journal plugin:
	- turn into proper list

EMR exporters:
	- refactor into formatters, make more generic
	- have one exporter that supports several target formats

progress note input:
- add NotebookProgressNoteInput class
- configurable popup keywords
- make popups non-modal
- allowing renaming episode from STC header
- make problem list an issue-episode shallow tree ?

forms layer
- generic forms GUI (edit area ?)

active patient privacy dilemma
- find a sane way preventing patients waiting in the exam room
  to freely glean other people's details

patient search/active patient
- find a sane way to empty the client of any patient so people
  can't casually glance over other 

